---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import paulaPortrait from '../assets/photos/paula-portrait.jpg';
const BASE = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---
<Layout title="About Paula Leech — Sex Therapist & Supervisor">

  <!-- HERO — full-bleed editorial header -->
  <section class="pl-page-hero pl-page-hero--about pl-reveal">
    <div class="pl-page-hero-art" aria-hidden="true">
      <img src={paulaPortrait.src} alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="pl-page-hero-inner">
      <p class="pl-label pl-page-hero-kicker">About</p>
      <h1 class="pl-page-hero-title">
        Why I'm<br/><em>here.</em>
      </h1>
      <ul class="pl-page-hero-offerings" aria-label="Practice">
        <li>
          <span class="pl-page-hero-off-num">01</span>
          <span class="pl-page-hero-off-label">Sex Therapist</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="pl-page-hero-off-num">02</span>
          <span class="pl-page-hero-off-label">CST-S Supervisor</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="pl-page-hero-off-num">03</span>
          <span class="pl-page-hero-off-label">Author</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="pl-page-hero-sub">
        LMFT · AASECT-certified · MA, OR &amp; NY · 10+ years in private practice.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BIO — two paragraphs lifted + lightly tightened from her current site -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] px-12 lg:px-20 mt-32 md:mt-40 pl-reveal">
    <div class="pl-grid items-start">
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4">
        <span class="pl-label">The path</span>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-8 mt-6 md:mt-0">
        <p style="
          font-family: var(--font-display);
          font-weight: 400;
          font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.4vw, 2rem);
          line-height: 1.4;
          letter-spacing: -0.015em;
          color: var(--color-ink);
        ">
          I trained as a marriage and family therapist at UMass Boston, then certified through AASECT as a sex therapist and, later, a supervisor of sex therapists. For over a decade I ran a private practice in Quincy, Massachusetts and co-founded a sex therapy agency and training institute &mdash; seeing clients while also training therapists to become competent, confident sex therapists themselves.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-8" style="
          font-family: var(--font-display);
          font-style: italic;
          font-weight: 400;
          font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw, 1.65rem);
          line-height: 1.5;
          letter-spacing: -0.01em;
          color: var(--color-ink-soft);
        ">
          I truly love this work. I love the adventure of moving relationships and individuals toward a greater sense of intimacy &mdash; the kind that can keep growing alongside us. I'm inspired by the transformation of therapists themselves as they witness and become part of fantastic change in their clients. And I never tire of learning, alongside and from both professionals and fellow sexuality enthusiasts, about this extraordinary corner of human life.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CREDENTIALS — manuscript ledger, reusing the home pattern -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] px-12 lg:px-20 mt-32 md:mt-40 pl-reveal">
    <div class="pl-grid items-start">
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4">
        <span class="pl-label">Credentials</span>
        <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.25rem); line-height: 0.95; margin-top: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: -0.025em;">
          Education &amp;<br/><em style="font-weight: 400;">certification.</em>
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-8 mt-10 md:mt-0">
        <div class="pl-ledger-manuscript pl-ledger-manuscript--about">
          <div class="pl-ledger-row">
            <span class="pl-ledger-date">CSTS</span>
            <span class="pl-ledger-title">Certified Supervisor of Sex Therapy<span class="pl-ledger-tag">AASECT</span></span>
            <span class="pl-ledger-price">Since 2018</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pl-ledger-row">
            <span class="pl-ledger-date">CST</span>
            <span class="pl-ledger-title">Certified Sex Therapist<span class="pl-ledger-tag">AASECT</span></span>
            <span class="pl-ledger-price">Since 2012</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pl-ledger-row">
            <span class="pl-ledger-date">LMFT</span>
            <span class="pl-ledger-title">Licensed Marriage &amp; Family Therapist<span class="pl-ledger-tag">MA · OR · NY</span></span>
            <span class="pl-ledger-price">Since 2009</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pl-ledger-row">
            <span class="pl-ledger-date">MA</span>
            <span class="pl-ledger-title">Marriage &amp; Family Therapy<span class="pl-ledger-tag">UMass Boston</span></span>
            <span class="pl-ledger-price">Graduate</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pl-ledger-row">
            <span class="pl-ledger-date">BS</span>
            <span class="pl-ledger-title">Family &amp; Human Development<span class="pl-ledger-tag">Arizona State</span></span>
            <span class="pl-ledger-price">Undergraduate</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PHILOSOPHY -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] px-12 lg:px-20 mt-40 md:mt-56 relative pl-reveal">
    <div class="relative">
      <div class="pl-grid">
        <div class="col-span-12 md:col-start-3 md:col-span-8">
          <p style="
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
            line-height: 1.3;
            letter-spacing: -0.018em;
            color: var(--color-ink);
          ">
            Our sexuality is interwoven into everything else we are. It's something we spend our whole lives trying to make sense of, in the middle of silence and a sex-negative world &mdash; immensely complex, particularly susceptible to shame and pressure and <em>should</em>. And yet it's one of the primary ways we express and receive love. Therapy is a way to tap into the freedom and joy of unraveling ourselves from all of that.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LOCATIONS / SPECIALTIES — split block -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] px-12 lg:px-20 mt-32 md:mt-40 pl-reveal">
    <div class="pl-grid items-start" style="row-gap: 3rem;">
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6">
        <span class="pl-label">Where I work</span>
        <h3 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.6vw, 2.25rem); line-height: 1.1; margin-top: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: -0.015em;">
          Therapy, supervision, training.
        </h3>
        <ul class="mt-6" style="color: var(--color-ink-soft); font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.7;">
          <li>Therapy: <strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">MA, OR, NY</strong> (virtual) &middot; <strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">in-person in Oregon only</strong></li>
          <li>Supervision: <strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">Worldwide</strong> (Zoom)</li>
          <li>Trainings at universities, institutes, and agencies across the US &amp; Canada</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6">
        <span class="pl-label">Clinical Areas of Specialization</span>
        <h3 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.6vw, 2.25rem); line-height: 1.1; margin-top: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: -0.015em;">
          What I work with.
        </h3>

        <div class="pl-specialties mt-8">
          <div class="pl-spec-group">
            <span class="pl-spec-heading">Identity &amp; orientation</span>
            <ul class="pl-spec-list">
              <li>LGBTQ+</li>
              <li>Gender identity &amp; sexual orientation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="pl-spec-group">
            <span class="pl-spec-heading">Desire &amp; arousal</span>
            <ul class="pl-spec-list">
              <li>Low / no desire</li>
              <li>Desire discrepancy in relationships</li>
              <li>Difficulty reaching orgasm</li>
              <li>Erectile dysfunction</li>
              <li>&ldquo;Premature&rdquo; or early ejaculation</li>
              <li>Delayed ejaculation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="pl-spec-group">
            <span class="pl-spec-heading">Pain &amp; the body</span>
            <ul class="pl-spec-list">
              <li>Vaginismus</li>
              <li>Sexual pain</li>
              <li>Sexual trauma</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="pl-spec-group">
            <span class="pl-spec-heading">Relationships</span>
            <ul class="pl-spec-list">
              <li>Infidelity</li>
              <li>Non-monogamy</li>
              <li>Kink &amp; BDSM</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="pl-spec-group">
            <span class="pl-spec-heading">Behavior</span>
            <ul class="pl-spec-list">
              <li>&ldquo;Sex addiction,&rdquo; porn &ldquo;addiction,&rdquo; or sexual compulsivity</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="pl-spec-group">
            <span class="pl-spec-heading">Across the lifespan</span>
            <ul class="pl-spec-list">
              <li>Developmental sexuality (children &amp; teens)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA — color-blocked triptych -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] px-12 lg:px-20 mt-40 md:mt-56 mb-32 pl-reveal">
    <h2 class="pl-cta-heading">
      Let's <em>begin.</em>
    </h2>
    <div class="pl-cta-triptych">
      <a href={`${BASE}/work-with-paula#therapy`} class="pl-cta-panel pl-cta-panel--plum">
        <span class="pl-cta-num">01 · Practice</span>
        <span class="pl-cta-label">Therapy</span>
        <span class="pl-cta-arrow">Begin →</span>
      </a>
      <a href={`${BASE}/work-with-paula#supervision`} class="pl-cta-panel pl-cta-panel--honey">
        <span class="pl-cta-num">02 · Mentor</span>
        <span class="pl-cta-label">Supervision</span>
        <span class="pl-cta-arrow">Apply →</span>
      </a>
      <a href={`${BASE}/courses`} class="pl-cta-panel pl-cta-panel--blue">
        <span class="pl-cta-num">03 · Learn</span>
        <span class="pl-cta-label">Trainings</span>
        <span class="pl-cta-arrow">Browse →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .pl-portrait {
    position: relative;
    display: block;
  }
  .pl-portrait-img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-left: auto;
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 40px 80px -32px rgba(42, 56, 24, 0.35);
    filter: contrast(0.97) saturate(0.92);
  }
  .pl-portrait-eyes {
    position: absolute;
    top: -2.5rem;
    left: -1.5rem;
    width: clamp(90px, 11vw, 160px);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .pl-portrait-eyes img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    mix-blend-mode: multiply;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
</style>
